divs: Sighting DetailsI've attached the original video, a digital video of a near infrared webcam, which shows a classic, saucer shaped UFO that moves into the picture 2.41 minutes into the video, makes a turn towards the east. The second event is two UFOs flying in formation 104 seconds after first event - these UFO are also moving east at extremely high speed Please open the edited for brevity video, unless you wish to be bored by the original waiting for the UFOs to pop up.
